" Faster browsing
nmap J 5j
nmap K 5k
vmap J 5j
vmap K 5k

" Split navigations
nnoremap <C-J> <C-W><C-J>
nnoremap <C-K> <C-W><C-K>
nnoremap <C-L> <C-W><C-L>
nnoremap <C-H> <C-W><C-H>

" TAB in general mode will move to text buffer
nnoremap <TAB> :bnext<CR>
" SHIFT-TAB will go back
nnoremap <S-TAB> :bprevious<CR>
